      • getProperty

        public <O> O getProperty(TitanKey key)
        Description copied from interface: TitanElement
        Retrieves the value associated with the given key on this vertex and casts it to the specified type. If the key is single-valued, then there can be at most one value and this value is returned (or null). If the key is list-valued, then a list of all associated values is returned, or an empty list of non exist.

        Specified by:
        getProperty in interface TitanElement
        Parameters:
        key - key
        Returns:
        value or list of values associated with key
